<DOCNO> NYT19980617.0077 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-06-17 11:13 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A3004 &Cx1f; ttj-z
u a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-CPT-COMPUTER-COLUMN-H     06-17 0961
