<P>
   &UR; EDITORS: In time for the traditional wedding season, The New York
Times Syndicate offers different perspectives on matrimony, both
humorous and practical.
</P>
<P>
   _ WEDDINGS UNDER THE INFLUENCE OF MURPHY'S LAW
</P>
<P>
   _ TOP 10 WEDDING MYTHS
</P>
<P>
   _ GETTING ALONG WITH THE IN-LAWS
</P>
<P>
   _ NEWLYWEDS' GUIDE TO DOMESTIC HARMONY
