<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-06-17 13:28 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A3238 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u k &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-MCNAMARA-COLUMN-BOS &LR;      06-17 0764
