<P>
   SEXTON-POEMS (Undated) -- Poems by the ``Mad Poets Society.''
</P>
<P>
   TV-RUSSIA (Undated) -- ``The Face of Russia,'' a three-part TV
series that airs on PBSfor three Wednesdays, presents a grand
collage of images and sounds, a millennium's worth. by Christine
Temin.
</P>
<P>
   MAGAZINE-REVIEW (Undated) _ To the veritable haberdashery of
hats worn with distinction by Jules Feiffer _ cartoonist,
screenwriter, playwright, novelist _ we can now add one more:
editor. By Don Aucoin.
