BLUES-TV (Los Angeles) _ Nickelodeon's ``Blues clues'' was the
primetime winner among kids 2-11 on Sunday against everything from
NBA championships to Wonderful World of Disney. An astounding feat,
if you consider the competition. By Keith Marder. 
. 
XFILES-MUSIC (Los Angeles) _ A review of the X Files soundtrack. By
Fred Shuster. 
. 
BUGS-MARATHON (Los Angeles) _ Nyaaaahh, what's up, Doc? It's
