today for use by NYTimes News Service clients. They will move in
the ``l'' lifestyle news file. For questions, contact Jimmy Johnson
at the Daily News, (818) 713-3695. 
. 
DAD-DAY (Los Angeles) _ Actor/director James Keach was recently
honored as a Father of the Year by the L.A. Father's Day Council at
the Beverly Hilton. He, his father and the family reminisce about
father-son moments. The lessons learned on both sides of the
fatherhood fence. By Barbara De Witt. 
. 
DAD-ADVICE (Los Angeles) _ A short list of fatherly advice, as told
by the Keaches. By Barbara De Witt. 
. 
DAD-LIST (Los Angeles) _ Thought Mom was hard to buy for? Now try
Dad. Here's help: a father's day gift guide. By Barbara De Witt. 
. 

