<HEADLINE>
FATHERLY ADVICE
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
By BARBARA DE WITT 
c.1998 Los Angeles Daily News  
<TEXT>
<P>
   LOS ANGELES _ Honesty is always the best policy. &QL; 
_ Always try your best. &QL; 
_ When your children stray off the path, be there when they fall. &QL; 
_ Let your children know you're not perfect. &QL; 
_ Practice Tough Love, when needed. &QL; 
_ Attend their plays, dances, ball games. &QL; 
_ Plan family outings, such as theater, camping, picnics. &QL; 
_ Be happy with whatever gift they give you, whether it's a poem or
a hammock or an ugly tie. &QL; 
_ James Keach and Stacy Keach Sr. &QR;
</P>
</TEXT>
