</P>
<P>
   $20 _ Pilsner glass accented with wild animal head by Arthur
Court, at Macy's.
</P>
<P>
   $20 _ ``I Love Dad'' and ``Godzilla'' ties (he'll wear it for
you), at Sears, Spencer Gifts, Tie Rack stores.
</P>
<P>
   $24.99 _ Black &AMP; Decker 45-piece Scorpion drilling combo set, at
Target and hardware stores.
</P>
<P>
   $24.99 _ Khaki trousers with (new-again) flat front, at Sears.
</P>
<P>
   $25 _ Millennium 2000 Countdown clock, at Robinsons-May.
</P>
<P>
   $25 _ A cooking class at the Stinking Rose restaurant in Beverly
Hills. To sign him up, call (310) 652-7673.
</P>
<P>
   $28.99 _ A new pair of Levi's 550 jeans, at J.C. Penney.
</P>
<P>
   $29.99 _ Vanguard binoculars for ballgames and the Hollywood
Bowl, at Kmart.
</P>
<P>
   $30 _ Tucker's Burnguard Oven Mitt for barbecuing, at
Restoration Hardware stores.
</P>
<P>
   $35 _ Novelty photo frames, at Bloomingdale's.
</P>
