   $37.99 _ TripMaker Deluxe, a computer program to map out your
family vacation, at CompUSA stores.
</P>
<P>
   $40 _ Snazzy silver cigar rest, at Bloomingdale's.
</P>
<P>
   $48 _ Callaway Golf Caddy, a collection of skin-care products
that clip onto a golf bag, at Nordstrom.
</P>
<P>
   $50 _ Warner Bros. talking watches featuring the voice of Mel
Blanc, at Mervyn's and other department stores.
</P>
<P>
   $58 _ Shop-Vac wet/dry vacuum for his workshop, at Target.
</P>
<P>
   $99.99 _ Gold ``Dad'' signet ring, at Sears.
</P>
<P>
   $99.99 _ Sony Watchman with teeny color TV, at Target.
</P>
<P>
   $149 _ Sony digital PCS phone with voice mail, call waiting and
three-way calling, from Sprint.
</P>
<P>
   $149 _ For his wood-paneled office, a retro-inspired brass desk
lamp with green shade, at Bombay stores.
</P>
<P>
   $190 _ Palm Pilot Personal Organizer, so he won't forget to pick
up the dry cleaning or take the team for pizza, at Bloomingdale's.
</P>
