</P>
<P>
   -- ``Mighty Aphrodite'' As Woody Allen's neurotic, complaining
wife.
</P>
<P>
   -- ``Twelfth Night'' As a lovelorn woman infatuated by another
woman, dressed as a man.
</P>
<P>
   -- ``Margaret's Museum'' Wife of a miner in a town whose men
risk their lives digging for coal.
