 Wednesday, June 17, 1998 
<TEXT>
<P>
   &UR; Editors: &LR;  &QC;
</P>
<P>
   JASPER-OTWELL (Jasper, Texas.) will not move tonight on The
Hearst News Service.
</P>
<P>
   Houston Chronicle.
</P>
</TEXT>
