<P>
   Here is the daily CoxNet budget for Cox papers of Thursday, June
18. This budget will be updated as necessary based on news
developments. Budget lines include information about what paper
originated a story and whether a story has a related photo, graphic
or page layout. Stories that have photos, graphics or page layouts
will be marked with PHOTO, GRAPHIC or LAYOUT. Those elements will
be posted on the Cox Server in folders matching the category and
slug of the story. All times are Eastern unless otherwise noted.
</P>
<P>
   If stories will move after 8 p.m. Eastern, an ETA will be given.
If stories, photos, graphics or layouts will not move or will move
late, we'll send an advisory on the wire.
</P>
